## 核心 Token

### 背景

| 用途 | 亮色 | 暗色 |
|------|------|------|
| Full Card | `bg-white/40` | `dark:bg-white/5` |
| Compact Row / Pill | `bg-white/30` | `dark:bg-white/5` |
| Header | `bg-white/30` | `dark:bg-black/30` |
| Pill（TagPill）| `bg-white/40` | `dark:bg-white/10` |

### 邊框

- 一般：`border border-white/30 dark:border-white/10`
- Compact Row：`border border-white/20 dark:border-white/10`

### 模糊

- Full Card：`backdrop-blur-2xl`
- Compact Row / Pill / Header：`backdrop-blur-md`

### 陰影

| 元素 | 靜止 | Hover |
|------|------|-------|
| Full Card | `shadow-[0_8px_32px_0_rgba(31,38,135,0.37)]` | `shadow-[0_16px_48px_0_rgba(31,38,135,0.5)]` |
| Compact Row | `shadow-[0_4px_16px_0_rgba(31,38,135,0.15)]` | `shadow-[0_8px_24px_0_rgba(31,38,135,0.25)]` |
| Pill | `shadow-[0_2px_8px_0_rgba(31,38,135,0.15)]` | `shadow-[0_4px_12px_0_rgba(31,38,135,0.25)]` |

### 內發光環

```
ring-1 ring-inset ring-white/30 dark:ring-white/10
```

Compact Row 略輕：`ring-white/25 dark:ring-white/10`

### 噪訊層（磨砂感）

```
absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.03] pointer-events-none
bg-[url('/noise.svg')] bg-repeat bg-[length:256px_256px]
```

> 使用 `.svg`，不是 `.png`

### 強調色漸層

- 文字（Hero h1）：`from-indigo-600 via-purple-600 to-pink-600 dark:from-indigo-300 dark:via-purple-300 dark:to-pink-300`
- 背景 overlay：`from-indigo-500/10 via-purple-500/5 to-pink-500/10`

---

## 三層結構（所有玻璃容器必備）

```
1. [選用] 漸層 overlay  — absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-500/10 ...
2. 內發光環            — absolute inset-0 rounded-{size} ring-1 ring-inset ring-white/30 ...
3. 噪訊磨砂層          — absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.03] bg-[url('/noise.svg')] ...
4. 內容層              — relative z-10
```

> 容器本身必須有 `relative overflow-hidden`

