## 三種卡片變體

### Full Card（PostCard、PostArticle、Hero）

```tsx
<article className="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/30 dark:border-white/10
  bg-white/40 dark:bg-white/5 p-6
  shadow-[0_8px_32px_0_rgba(31,38,135,0.37)] backdrop-blur-2xl
  transition-all duration-300
  hover:bg-white/50 dark:hover:bg-white/10
  hover:shadow-[0_16px_48px_0_rgba(31,38,135,0.5)] hover:-translate-y-0.5">
  <div className="absolute inset-0 rounded-2xl ring-1 ring-inset ring-white/30 dark:ring-white/10 pointer-events-none" />
  <div className="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.03] pointer-events-none bg-[url('/noise.svg')] bg-repeat bg-[length:256px_256px]" />
  <div className="relative z-10">{/* 內容 */}</div>
</article>
```

### Compact Row（首頁文章列表）

```tsx
<Link className="group block rounded-xl border border-white/20 dark:border-white/10
  bg-white/30 dark:bg-white/5 px-5 py-4
  shadow-[0_4px_16px_0_rgba(31,38,135,0.15)] backdrop-blur-md
  ring-1 ring-inset ring-white/25 dark:ring-white/10
  hover:bg-white/50 dark:hover:bg-white/10
  hover:shadow-[0_8px_24px_0_rgba(31,38,135,0.25)]
  transition-all duration-300">
```

### Pill（TagPill、GitHub 按鈕）

```tsx
<Link className="rounded-full border border-white/30 dark:border-white/10
  bg-white/40 dark:bg-white/10
  px-3 py-0.5 backdrop-blur-md
  ring-1 ring-inset ring-white/30 dark:ring-white/10
  shadow-[0_2px_8px_0_rgba(31,38,135,0.15)]
  hover:bg-white/60 dark:hover:bg-white/20
  hover:shadow-[0_4px_12px_0_rgba(31,38,135,0.25)]
  transition-all duration-300">
```

